\par\par Are you for or against the \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 Occupy Central\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0  civil disobedience protest? This is now the question on everyone's lips. Even family members and friends are asking each other this question. There is disagreement among many family members and friends. Many of my friends have told me there are a lot of angry arguments in their families. Some family members support \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 Occupy Central\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0  while others oppose it. The civil disobedience protest has alienated family members and friends. When a question or an issue is on everyone's lips it means a lot of people are talking about it. Most Hong Kong people are now talking about the \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 Occupy Central\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0  protest. It is on everyone's lips.     \par\par   The word alien has many meanings. Something that is unfamiliar or strange can be described as alien. For example, hairy crabs are common here but would be considered alien （unfamiliar） in the US although some have been found in rivers there. Things from a foreign country, such as a culture, can also be called alien. For example, many Chinese people consider the African culture as alien， and Africans consider the Chinese culture as alien. In the US, illegal immigrants are called illegal aliens. We don't know if other planets have living things but in science fiction movies and novels people from other planets are called aliens.\par\par   The word "alienate" （verb） has a different meaning. If you alienate your friends or family members, it means you cause them to become unfriendly or unsupportive of you. For example, if your girlfriend supports \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 Occupy Central\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0  but you do not, you can alienate her by angrily telling her she is wrong to support \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 Occupy Central\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0 . Friends who become alienated with each other by always arguing will often not remain friends any more. A friend of mine told me he alienated his brother so much while arguing over \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 Occupy Central\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0  that they don't even talk anymore. Have you alienated your family members by arguing about whether or not to support \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 Occupy Central\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0 ？***\par\par   你支持抑或反对\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 占中\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0 公民抗命示威？这是人人挂在口边（on everyone's lips）的问题，甚至在家人和朋友间也互相问着这道问题，家人和朋友间不时想法分歧。有不少朋友告诉我，家中出现激烈争论，有些家庭成员支持\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 占中\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0 ，又有其他的反对。公民抗命示威已然离间了（alienated）家人和朋友。当一个问题或议题是on everyone's lips，是指有许多人在谈论着它。大部份香港人都在谈论着\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 占中\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0 示威，因此它是城中热话（on everyone's lips）。\par\par   Alien这个字有多重意思。某样陌生或怪异的事情也可被形容为alien。譬如，大闸蟹在这里很常见，但在美国就会被视为异禀（alien），即使那边的河域也能找到毛蟹。外国的东西，例如文化，也会被说成是alien。例如，许多中国人将非洲文化视为异族的（alien），同样非洲人也会将中国文化视为异族的（alien）。在美国，非法入境者会被称为illegal aliens。我们不晓得其他星球上是否存在着生物，但在科幻电影和小说里，来自其他星球的人就会被称为外星人（aliens）。\par\par   动词Alienate有几个意思，若你alienate你的朋友或家人，即是你在疏远他们，令他们对你不再友善或支持。例如，若你女友支持\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 占中\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0 而你不是，你可愤而说她支持\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 占中\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0 是错的，与她不和（alienate）。因着激烈争拗而彼此不和（alienated）的朋友，通常都不能再做朋友。有一位朋友跟我说，他因为争论\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 占中\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0 而疏远（alienated）了他的兄弟，甚至不再谈话。你有没有因为支持\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b\cf6 占中\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\f15 \b0\cf0 与否，与你的家人闹不和（alienated）t\par\par   mickchug@gmail.com\par\par   中译：七刻Michael Chugani 褚简宁 \par\par    \par
